{"id":4395,"date":"2025-06-20T17:37:12","date_gmt":"2025-06-20T10:37:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4395"},"modified":"2025-11-18T23:11:26","modified_gmt":"2025-11-18T16:11:26","slug":"workshop-giai-phap-tang-sac-to-phuc-hoi-da-sau-viem","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/workshop-giai-phap-tang-sac-to-phuc-hoi-da-sau-viem\/","title":{"rendered":"Workshop: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 &#038; ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau vi\u00eam"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u00e0nh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, k\u00e9o theo nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong \u0111\u00f3, x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam (PIH) v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da sau x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c Spa, Th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, GSC t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trang b\u1ecb ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c spa\/ th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 \u2013 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 Spa, b\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh n\u00e2ng cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p an to\u00e0n, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, c\u00f3 t\u00ednh \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng cao trong \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4399\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4399\" style=\"width: 720px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4399\" title=\"Workshop: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam &amp;amp; t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/HINH-2.7-1920-x-1200-1024x640.webp\" alt=\"Workshop: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam &amp; t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da\" width=\"720\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/HINH-2.7-1920-x-1200-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/HINH-2.7-1920-x-1200-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/HINH-2.7-1920-x-1200-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/HINH-2.7-1920-x-1200-1536x960.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/HINH-2.7-1920-x-1200-600x375.webp 600w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/HINH-2.7-1920-x-1200.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4399\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Workshop: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam &amp; t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thong-tin-chi-tiet-chuong-trinh\"><\/span><b>Th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Link Zoom<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/us06web.zoom.us\/j\/85970467491?pwd=Y6psgG0s1AzzyPGemy1EETbtobayad.1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e2y<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Th\u1eddi gian<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: 20h00 \u2013 21h30, Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 24 th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2025<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng qua n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng Zoom<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Chi ph\u00ed tham gia<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd tham gia<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/forms.gle\/ZRMcFbBQvmXGnb2z9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>C\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Zalo GSC \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/zalo.me\/g\/aihdok555\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tham gia nh\u00f3m Zalo<\/span><\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-nen-tham-gia\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00ean tham gia<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee7 Spa v\u00e0 Th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n mong mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb, gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00e1c s\u0129, d\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u c\u1ea7n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da sau li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang kh\u1edfi nghi\u1ec7p trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhung-van-de-pho-bien-duoc-giai-quyet-trong-chuong-trinh\"><\/span><b>Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng g\u1eb7p t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m ho\u1eb7c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau c\u00e1c li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 l\u0103n kim, peel da, laser ho\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec7n di. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u00e0 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o c\u01a1 s\u1edf d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f3a \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o n\u00e0y s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u1ec1:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam (PIH) v\u00e0 c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da sau can thi\u1ec7p x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p khi \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da tr\u1edf n\u00ean nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Quy tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e2n t\u00edch v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gia-tri-thuc-tien-tu-chuong-trinh\"><\/span><b>Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n t\u1eeb ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft. N\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean kinh nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng case study \u0111\u00e3 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i h\u01a1n 500 Spa v\u00e0 Th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c. V\u1edbi th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 90 ph\u00fat, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 trong 10 \u2013 28 ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb \u0111\u00fang theo c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh Spa, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 quy m\u00f4 nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf m\u00e0 Spa \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4396\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4396\" style=\"width: 720px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4396\" title=\"Workshop: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam &amp;amp; t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/1920x1200-300x188.webp\" alt=\"Workshop: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam &amp; t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da\" width=\"720\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/1920x1200-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/1920x1200-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/1920x1200-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/1920x1200-1536x960.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/1920x1200-600x375.webp 600w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/1920x1200.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4396\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Workshop: Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam &amp; t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-ngu-giang-vien-giau-kinh-nghiem\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0 hai chuy\u00ean gia h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 H\u1ed3ng Ng\u1ecdc<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u2013 Tr\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u00f3m nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea1i GSC, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c Spa v\u00e0 th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Chuy\u00ean gia Ng\u1ecdc Th\u01a1<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u2013 Gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho h\u01a1n 200 Spa, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1edd ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u, s\u00e1t v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"quyen-loi-dac-biet-danh-cho-hoc-vien\"><\/span><b>Quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi tham gia kh\u00f3a \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ed9 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u v\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 chu\u1ea9n y khoa.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Quy tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb chu\u1ea9n h\u00f3a, \u0111\u00e3 qua ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c Spa GSC chuy\u1ec3n giao.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Voucher \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i 5% v\u00e0 qu\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng cao c\u1ea5p t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u GSC.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham gia c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i chia s\u1ebb chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Spa tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"loi-ket\"><\/span><b>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ng\u00e0nh l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u00e2ng cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t gi\u00fap Spa v\u00e0 Th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf, gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn do GSC t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 Spa, b\u00e1c s\u0129, d\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1eebng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng nhi\u1ec1u gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb n\u00e0y \u2013 h\u00e3y \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd ngay h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o su\u1ea5t tham gia, v\u00ec s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp thu v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0nh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nhanh, \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi. Trong \u0111\u00f3, x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da sau x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c Spa, Th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan t\u00e2m.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":4397,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4395","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4395","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4395"}],"version-history":[{"count":12,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4395\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4478,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4395\/revisions\/4478"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4397"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4395"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4395"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4395"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}